responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "F087EDD945C34CA6981561ABAB9E9E38", "I appreciate the Court following up on my lead, but for all that is holy, please don\'t hassle my farmhands, they\'re good lads.Talk to my daughter, I get the idea she knows more than she wants to tell me about our slippery fellow.")
